  "texts": [
    "In t-th round, for a pairwise response (s 1 t, s 2 t |s <t), the ranking loss is defined as:",
    "min(0, P(s 2 t) -P(s 1 t)).",
    "The final loss function L is a combination of the cross-entropy loss and ranking loss:",
    "Here, β is a hyperparameter.",
    "We use the G3 split of ToolBench (Qin et al., 2023) as a seed to construct the MGToolBench dataset, which contains 75,888 solution steps for Stage 1 SFT model training."
